</script><div style="margin-top:.5rem;font-size:.78rem;color:#888;text-align:center">View larger map</div></div></section><footer style="background:#1C1917;color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);padding:2rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;font-size:.92rem">Juneau Alaska, USA · <a href="mailto:info@geotechnicalengineering.sbs" style="color:#FFF;text-decoration:underline">info@geotechnicalengineering.sbs</a><div data-authority-refs class="authority-refs" style="text-align:center;font-size:.8rem;padding:.5rem 0;opacity:.6"><strong>References:</strong>ASTM Standards · USACE Engineer Manuals · ISO Geotechnical</div><div class="updated-info" data-updated="2026-03-25" style="text-align:center;font-size:.85rem;opacity:.7;padding:.5rem 0">Last updated: 2026-03-25</div></footer></body></html>